When should you still throw?

Keep throw new RuntimeException(...) only for transient problems where retry could fix it:
	•	Cosmos DB/Service Bus/HTTP timeouts
	•	Temporary throttling (429)
	•	Network hiccups
	•	Notification API returns 5xx and you have retry policy

For all permanent problems (bad schema, missing required fields, invalid business rules), log to error blob and return.

